&lt;ol>
 

 &lt;li>Analyse marginal changes in ethnic residential segregation due to changes in the population definition and data quality between 1991 and 2001.&lt;br />&lt;/li>

 &lt;li>Test the sensitivity of indices of segregation to boundary changes between 1991 and 2001 and since 2001.&lt;br />&lt;/li>

 &lt;li>Examine ethnic residential segregation by age cohorts using complete mid-1991 and mid-2001 population estimates.&lt;br />&lt;/li>
